IN RE: Rebecca Lynn VISHNEFSKI NO. 2018-OB-1801 Supreme Court of Louisiana. December 3, 2018

ORDER

Considering the Petition for Transfer to Active Status filed by respondent, and the response thereto filed by the Office of Disciplinary Counsel,

IT IS ORDERED that Rebecca Lynn Vishnefski, Louisiana Bar Roll number 26965, be and she hereby is reinstated to active status pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 22(G). This order shall be effective immediately.
